snippet.title: RoboBlastPlanet launch TV Commercial (official version - Denmark)
snippet.description: Build your own robots and conquer the battlefield in this action-packed multiplayer game! Hear the crowd go bananas for the ultimate robot fighter! Download it from App Store or Google play, or play it on PC here: http://www.roboblastplanet.com/
